<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<head>
		<title>CSS Test: text-decoration-line - none - basic cases</title>
		<link rel="author" title="Makoto Kikuchi" href="mailto:kikuchi@est.co.jp" />
		<link rel="help" title="CSS Text Level 3: 11.1.1. Indent Text: the 'text-decoration-line' property" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css3-text/#text-decoration-line" />
